WEBVTT

01:37.940 --> 01:41.070
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.130 --> 01:44.000
[Episode 32]

01:46.430 --> 01:47.350
Our department

01:47.759 --> 01:50.220
doesn't expect you
to bring in huge results.

01:50.400 --> 01:51.560
Don't put too much pressure on yourself,

01:51.560 --> 01:52.400
okay?

01:53.640 --> 01:54.700
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

01:54.950 --> 01:56.150
I'll think about it.

01:56.640 --> 01:57.240
Good luck.

02:01.480 --> 02:03.150
Shanghai just opened

02:03.150 --> 02:04.950
a new AI industrial park.

02:05.120 --> 02:06.120
Have you heard?

02:06.150 --> 02:06.790
Yes.

02:07.350 --> 02:09.520
It seems a lot of new companies
have already moved in.

02:09.520 --> 02:10.120
What?

02:10.120 --> 02:11.520
Want to go get some deals?

02:11.750 --> 02:13.360
Forget it. It's so hot.

02:13.360 --> 02:14.360
Who wants to do cold visits?

02:14.360 --> 02:16.310
I haven't even finished my current orders.

02:16.310 --> 02:17.430
True.

02:19.530 --> 02:21.900
[Shanghai AI Industrial Park Unveiled]

02:39.630 --> 02:40.630
Working so hard?

02:42.190 --> 02:43.840
You didn't even check your phone.

02:43.840 --> 02:45.120
Why are you here?

02:47.600 --> 02:49.300
[Ji Feng]

02:49.300 --> 02:50.250
[Let's go eat something good later.]

02:50.270 --> 02:51.120
[Are you off work yet?]

02:51.840 --> 02:53.900
I was just preparing some materials.

02:54.190 --> 02:56.390
You've been on the phone all day, right?

02:57.310 --> 02:58.310
Throat lozenges.

02:59.400 --> 03:01.280
This is just what I need.

03:05.190 --> 03:07.280
These are sales portfolios.

03:07.470 --> 03:09.130
You're going for cold visits?

03:09.310 --> 03:10.190
I recently found out

03:10.190 --> 03:12.310
about this new AI park.

03:12.310 --> 03:13.310
I want to check it out.

03:13.310 --> 03:15.840
I think there could
be a lot of opportunities.

03:15.910 --> 03:17.470
Then you need to rest well.

03:18.400 --> 03:20.840
How about this? Let's call it a day.

03:20.840 --> 03:22.570
Let's go out for some fresh air.

03:23.630 --> 03:24.400
Mr. Ji?

03:29.079 --> 03:31.190
I'm here to see Director Qian.

03:32.400 --> 03:35.190
Director Qian got off work
a long time ago.

03:35.910 --> 03:38.040
It's fine. I'll come back another day.

03:38.910 --> 03:39.750
Okay.

04:09.280 --> 04:12.560
In 100 meters, turn right
onto West Cuidie Road.

04:41.830 --> 04:43.159
What are you doing here?

04:45.270 --> 04:47.390
I'm here as your assistant.

04:49.000 --> 04:49.870
Let me.

04:56.000 --> 04:57.360
How did you think of

04:57.360 --> 04:58.830
this new AI track?

05:00.270 --> 05:02.120
I noticed
the sales department's client list

05:02.120 --> 05:03.830
hasn't been updated in a long time.

05:03.830 --> 05:06.000
I wanted to see
if there are new possibilities.

05:06.000 --> 05:08.110
And with AI being such a hot topic lately,

05:07.910 --> 05:09.820
♪ Life is full of ♪

05:08.390 --> 05:10.600
and this new industrial park just opening,

05:10.600 --> 05:12.240
I figured I'd come check it out.

05:10.870 --> 05:13.520
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

05:10.940 --> 05:12.130
[Xingyao Smart Control]

05:12.680 --> 05:15.050
How much do you know
about your potential clients?

05:15.050 --> 05:18.900
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

05:15.270 --> 05:15.830
Do you realize

05:15.830 --> 05:17.430
these companies are pretty small?

05:17.110 --> 05:18.130
[Taihui Zhiyuan]

05:18.000 --> 05:19.830
Do they have the ability

05:18.270 --> 05:21.060
[Xu Miyu, Sales Representative]

05:19.830 --> 05:20.950
or interest

05:20.490 --> 05:22.490
♪ All those confusions ♪

05:21.220 --> 05:24.790
[AI Intelligence]

05:21.270 --> 05:23.240
to afford a five-star hotel like Purong?

05:23.080 --> 05:26.800
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

05:23.510 --> 05:24.560
I know these companies

05:24.560 --> 05:26.360
are mostly in their startup phase.

05:26.360 --> 05:27.800
Their employees are young too.

05:27.680 --> 05:31.680
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

05:28.120 --> 05:30.120
They might be different from

05:30.120 --> 05:31.580
our traditional clients.

05:31.680 --> 05:33.000
But I believe they also have

05:31.870 --> 05:33.380
[Purong Hotel Room Overview]

05:33.000 --> 05:34.430
a need for hotel services.

05:33.440 --> 05:34.490
[Room Facilities and Experience]

05:34.830 --> 05:36.390
So I want to take the initiative now

05:35.080 --> 05:37.440
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

05:36.390 --> 05:37.520
to reach out to them,

05:37.830 --> 05:39.240
understand their

05:38.610 --> 05:40.680
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

05:39.240 --> 05:41.360
service needs and consumption habits,

05:41.360 --> 05:42.560
and adjust

05:42.350 --> 05:46.100
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

05:42.560 --> 05:44.090
our services accordingly.

05:44.390 --> 05:46.720
With the rise of the AI industry
in the future,

05:46.720 --> 05:47.680
our hotel could

05:47.680 --> 05:48.950
gain a new batch of clients.

05:47.720 --> 05:49.640
♪ Busy and restless ♪

05:49.120 --> 05:49.920
You're right.

05:50.280 --> 05:54.080
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

05:50.390 --> 05:51.390
Times have changed.

05:51.390 --> 05:53.250
The client base is also updating.

05:53.560 --> 05:55.390
So it's not just the sales department

05:55.070 --> 05:59.210
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

05:55.560 --> 05:57.159
that needs to develop new clients

05:57.159 --> 05:58.490
based on market trends.

05:58.500 --> 06:05.910
[Spiritual Cloud Atlas]

05:58.800 --> 05:59.800
Our entire hotel needs

05:59.800 --> 06:01.240
to keep exploring new tracks

06:01.000 --> 06:03.570
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

06:01.560 --> 06:02.800
and adjusting our service strategies

06:02.800 --> 06:04.530
to fit different client needs.

06:04.680 --> 06:06.770
♪ Don't look back ♪

06:05.340 --> 06:06.040
That's

06:06.600 --> 06:07.870
also a new challenge for me

06:07.680 --> 06:09.600
♪ I've already learned ♪

06:08.030 --> 06:09.360
as the general manager.

06:09.480 --> 06:10.480
So,

06:10.230 --> 06:14.030
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

06:10.600 --> 06:12.920
you're here doing market research today?

06:12.920 --> 06:13.500
Yes.

06:13.590 --> 06:14.650
[Spiritual Cloud Atlas]

06:14.040 --> 06:15.270
I think there are a lot of ways

06:14.760 --> 06:16.510
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

06:15.270 --> 06:17.460
AI and Purong
can work together in the future.

06:17.220 --> 06:21.410
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

06:17.680 --> 06:20.160
I'm not just talking about
offering them rooms

06:20.160 --> 06:21.240
or event space.

06:21.480 --> 06:23.590
We could also try
bringing more AI elements

06:22.140 --> 06:25.050
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

06:23.800 --> 06:25.020
into the hotel itself.

06:24.890 --> 06:28.530
[Spiritual Cloud Atlas]

06:25.920 --> 06:27.040
I also want to find out today

06:25.960 --> 06:28.290
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

06:27.040 --> 06:28.480
what new technologies they have

06:28.480 --> 06:30.600
that could be used in a hotel setting.

06:29.000 --> 06:30.510
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

06:31.160 --> 06:32.470
This could be a good opportunity

06:32.470 --> 06:34.000
for our hotel to transform.

06:34.730 --> 06:35.920
Then let's work together

06:35.920 --> 06:37.040
to win a new opportunity

06:37.040 --> 06:38.240
for Purong Hotel.

06:50.480 --> 06:51.120
So?

06:51.480 --> 06:53.920
How would you rate your little assistant?

06:55.680 --> 06:57.560
I was afraid you'd scare them.

06:57.560 --> 07:00.760
What kind of general manager
goes out to make cold visits?

07:01.480 --> 07:02.390
Well,

07:02.390 --> 07:05.160
I'm way more efficient with you here.

07:05.800 --> 07:07.600
How about hiring me officially?

07:12.260 --> 07:13.020
[Xue Rui]

07:15.240 --> 07:16.360
Answer it.

07:18.720 --> 07:19.480
Answer it.

07:22.320 --> 07:23.120
Wait a minute.

07:26.480 --> 07:27.240
Rui?

07:27.600 --> 07:28.440
Where are you?

07:29.480 --> 07:31.360
I'm on leave today.

07:32.530 --> 07:35.010
Mr. Liu, who contacted us
last time, is here.

07:36.680 --> 07:38.360
Why did he have to pick today?

07:39.490 --> 07:40.290
You should go.

07:40.480 --> 07:41.360
I've got this.

07:41.600 --> 07:42.159
Go ahead.

07:43.390 --> 07:44.920
Okay, I'm heading back now.

07:47.360 --> 07:48.820
It's fine, finish your meal. No rush.

07:48.820 --> 07:50.040
They're waiting for you.

07:50.040 --> 07:51.720
Work is important. Go now.

07:55.040 --> 07:55.600
Coffee.

07:55.620 --> 07:56.500
Okay.

07:57.260 --> 07:58.240
Drive safe.

07:58.680 --> 07:59.480
Call me if you need anything.

07:59.480 --> 08:00.010
Okay.

08:06.040 --> 08:08.120
Hello, do you have an appointment?

08:08.360 --> 08:09.800
I'm looking for-

08:09.800 --> 08:11.040
You can't come in without an appointment.

08:11.040 --> 08:12.970
Please make an appointment first.

08:13.240 --> 08:14.480
Look, I'm already here.

08:14.480 --> 08:16.480
Could you let me talk to someone

08:16.480 --> 08:17.160
from your contact team?

08:17.160 --> 08:18.480
May I ask who you are?

08:19.360 --> 08:21.800
I am a sales representative
from Purong Hotel.

08:21.800 --> 08:23.360
My name is Xu Miyu.

08:25.360 --> 08:26.300
Or maybe

08:26.360 --> 08:27.800
I can make an appointment for later today

08:27.800 --> 08:29.240
or tomorrow morning?

08:29.360 --> 08:30.920
Ma'am, here's the thing.

08:31.040 --> 08:32.909
We're a newly established small company.

08:32.909 --> 08:34.909
Our business volume is still very limited.

08:34.909 --> 08:35.669
How about this?

08:35.669 --> 08:37.360
You can leave your hotel materials here.

08:37.360 --> 08:38.669
If we need anything in the future,

08:38.669 --> 08:39.480
we will contact you.

08:39.480 --> 08:40.360
Would that work?

08:40.360 --> 08:41.360
Sure.

08:42.490 --> 08:43.130
Here it is.

08:44.790 --> 08:46.240
If you need anything,

08:46.260 --> 08:47.460
please do contact me.

08:48.480 --> 08:49.240
Goodbye.

08:49.240 --> 08:50.030
Take care.

08:54.390 --> 08:56.480
I'll wait for your good news, Mr. Ji.

08:56.480 --> 08:57.360
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

08:57.360 --> 09:00.220
We look forward to
working closely with you as well.

09:00.960 --> 09:02.910
I really hit it off with you, Mr. Ji.

09:04.130 --> 09:05.990
Look how long we've been talking—

09:06.030 --> 09:07.490
it's already dinner time.

09:07.550 --> 09:09.240
How about I treat?

09:09.240 --> 09:11.030
Let's grab a bite and have a few drinks.

09:11.030 --> 09:12.000
I think...

09:12.000 --> 09:13.030
I'm really sorry,

09:13.240 --> 09:15.550
but I still need to review
your company's proposal.

09:15.550 --> 09:16.000
Another day.

09:16.000 --> 09:17.730
I'll treat you some other time.

09:17.790 --> 09:20.690
You're indeed a legendary workaholic.

09:21.150 --> 09:23.150
Mr. Liu, let's do it some other time.

09:23.150 --> 09:24.600
We'll drink till we drop next time.

09:24.600 --> 09:25.910
Okay, let's get together next time.

09:25.910 --> 09:26.550
Okay.

09:27.410 --> 09:28.540
No need to see me out.

09:40.840 --> 09:41.600
Mr. Ji,

09:42.150 --> 09:42.910
it's after work hours now.

09:42.910 --> 09:43.480
Alright.

09:43.600 --> 09:44.360
I gotta go.

09:59.840 --> 10:01.570
Has any company contacted you?

10:08.860 --> 10:11.790
Don't lose hope.
Hard work always pays off.

10:12.790 --> 10:13.600
Really.

10:14.720 --> 10:15.840
Seeing you work so hard

10:15.840 --> 10:17.120
for your career,

10:18.000 --> 10:20.460
our sales department
is truly in good hands.

10:22.360 --> 10:23.840
When I used to do sales,

10:23.840 --> 10:26.370
I also got rejected
for over a month straight.

10:26.720 --> 10:27.980
But you have to believe

10:28.240 --> 10:29.500
that sales is all about

10:29.630 --> 10:32.000
quantity leading to quality.

10:32.470 --> 10:33.320
You...

10:34.360 --> 10:37.480
used to do sales too?

10:39.000 --> 10:40.190
I was amazing.

10:40.480 --> 10:43.720
I even got last place
in the annual performance ranking.

10:45.450 --> 10:47.840
That's probably
your most embarrassing moment, huh?

10:47.840 --> 10:48.790
Tell me about it.

10:51.480 --> 10:52.720
Just drop me off
at the intersection ahead.

10:52.720 --> 10:54.440
It's fine. I'll drop you off downstairs.

10:54.440 --> 10:55.240
Better not.

10:55.510 --> 10:57.120
If people see

10:57.120 --> 10:59.630
the general manager
taking me to the staff dorms,

10:59.630 --> 11:01.720
there'll be gossip everywhere tomorrow.

11:01.720 --> 11:02.600
Makes sense.

11:03.480 --> 11:04.750
Although there's no explicit rule

11:04.750 --> 11:06.350
against office romances...

11:07.240 --> 11:08.020
Yeah.

11:08.240 --> 11:09.750
It's a critical period now.

11:09.750 --> 11:11.360
So many eyes are on you.

11:11.480 --> 11:13.080
Better to keep a low profile.

11:13.720 --> 11:16.360
Plus, I just joined the sales department.

11:16.840 --> 11:19.640
I don't want to be looked down upon
because of this.

11:22.040 --> 11:23.760
Alright, got it.

11:27.000 --> 11:33.480
[School]

11:37.840 --> 11:38.970
Then I'll head back.

11:39.240 --> 11:40.240
See you tomorrow.

11:48.240 --> 11:49.360
Clocking out.

11:49.870 --> 11:50.630
Bye.

11:50.630 --> 11:51.170
Good night.

11:51.170 --> 11:51.930
Bye.

11:57.640 --> 11:58.400
Good night.

12:28.240 --> 12:29.240
Hello?

12:29.540 --> 12:30.670
Yes, it's me.

12:31.480 --> 12:33.600
Okay, I'll go over right now.

12:33.630 --> 12:34.750
Immediately.

12:48.990 --> 12:50.580
[Party A: Sheng Yi
Intelligent Technology Co., Ltd.]

12:49.640 --> 12:51.490
Sheng Yi Intelligent Technology?

12:50.610 --> 12:51.540
[Party B: Purong Hotel Co., Ltd.]

12:51.560 --> 12:52.420
[Authorized Representative: Xu Miyu]

12:53.870 --> 12:54.630
Not bad.

12:55.360 --> 12:57.240
100 room nights a year.

12:58.080 --> 12:59.510
It's not a big deal,

12:59.750 --> 13:00.750
but at least

13:00.750 --> 13:02.360
you've broken your zero.

13:03.840 --> 13:05.000
Thank you, Mr. Qian.

13:05.200 --> 13:06.530
I'll keep working hard.

13:07.630 --> 13:09.870
Since your first deal

13:09.870 --> 13:11.630
is about AI,

13:12.000 --> 13:14.360
I'll put you in charge of
the whole AI track.

13:14.360 --> 13:15.120
The higher-ups

13:15.120 --> 13:17.450
urge me to develop new business every day.

13:17.750 --> 13:19.120
You can take the lead.

13:19.910 --> 13:22.080
I will talk to HR today.

13:22.200 --> 13:25.840
Starting tomorrow,
you're the new business manager.

13:49.750 --> 13:51.880
I want to ask you something about work.

13:53.630 --> 13:56.000
I thought tonight was a date.

13:56.220 --> 13:58.630
It is a date.

13:59.870 --> 14:02.730
But this is really—

14:02.890 --> 14:03.760
I have to ask.

14:03.790 --> 14:04.940
Just this one question.

14:04.940 --> 14:06.810
I promise I'll stop after this.

14:06.870 --> 14:07.630
I promise.

14:10.420 --> 14:11.760
I'm just kidding.

14:12.480 --> 14:13.860
I heard.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.400
You made your first sale.

14:15.510 --> 14:17.240
100 room nights a year.

14:17.360 --> 14:19.120
And you didn't tell me the good news?

14:19.120 --> 14:20.820
What good news?

14:21.000 --> 14:22.570
It'd sound like a joke.

14:22.630 --> 14:24.440
I don't think it's a joke at all.

14:24.480 --> 14:27.340
Groundbreaking achievements
are always legends.

14:28.070 --> 14:30.730
The sales department
has gained another elite.

14:31.870 --> 14:33.540
You're exaggerating.

14:34.330 --> 14:35.240
But

14:36.870 --> 14:37.750
I don't know why—

14:37.750 --> 14:40.120
Mr. Qian's reaction really unsettled me.

14:41.600 --> 14:43.050
I feel like

14:43.120 --> 14:44.600
no matter how careful I am,

14:44.600 --> 14:46.510
I'm always part of his game.

14:47.320 --> 14:49.000
I'm afraid he's scheming against me.

14:49.000 --> 14:50.360
I'm also worried that every move I make

14:50.360 --> 14:51.240
will be used against me by him,

14:51.240 --> 14:53.080
and that it will affect
the hotel's operations

14:53.080 --> 14:54.760
and undermine your leadership.

14:54.760 --> 14:56.280
I approved your transfer,

14:56.310 --> 14:58.690
which means I believe
you already have the ability

14:58.690 --> 15:00.210
to face these risks.

15:00.480 --> 15:02.140
There's no need to be anxious.

15:02.240 --> 15:03.970
These things are unavoidable.

15:06.360 --> 15:09.000
Ji Feng, can you teach me

15:09.000 --> 15:10.120
what to do?

15:10.480 --> 15:12.480
This is a job that steps on people's toes.

15:12.480 --> 15:13.440
You said

15:13.510 --> 15:15.480
you understand
the products and the clients.

15:15.480 --> 15:17.240
That's your core competitiveness.

15:17.240 --> 15:19.120
Just work towards that goal.

15:21.000 --> 15:22.300
But what if...

15:22.330 --> 15:25.010
Whatever happens, I'll be here.

15:41.380 --> 15:44.230
[Innovation Hall]

15:44.610 --> 15:46.500
[Innovation Hall]

15:53.930 --> 15:57.720
[Innovation Hall]

16:04.600 --> 16:06.240
Hello. I'm looking for

16:06.240 --> 16:08.240
Manager Wu from Lubot.

16:11.940 --> 16:14.270
[Sheng Yi
Chairman]

16:24.840 --> 16:26.870
Are you Ms. Xu?

16:27.440 --> 16:28.600
You must be Manager Wu.

16:28.600 --> 16:29.360
I'm sorry.

16:29.360 --> 16:30.420
I'm not Manager Wu.

16:30.470 --> 16:31.500
Just call me Li.

16:31.630 --> 16:32.600
Hello.

16:33.210 --> 16:34.610
Manager Wu...

16:35.080 --> 16:36.480
Manager Wu is in a meeting

16:36.480 --> 16:37.940
and really can't get away.

16:38.200 --> 16:40.530
He asked me to come
and get your materials.

16:41.080 --> 16:42.280
Please wait a moment.

16:43.500 --> 16:47.150
[Xingyao Smart Control]

16:48.360 --> 16:50.360
Maybe I'll wait for him here.

16:50.360 --> 16:51.840
I know you're

16:51.840 --> 16:54.000
currently accepting bids
for event venues for the launch of

16:54.000 --> 16:55.320
your new generation Smart Agibot.

16:55.320 --> 16:56.080
Our Purong Hotel

16:56.080 --> 16:57.340
is truly a perfect fit.

16:57.720 --> 16:59.240
Telling me that won't help.

16:59.240 --> 17:00.120
Those decisions get made

17:00.120 --> 17:01.720
by the leaders in the conference room.

17:01.720 --> 17:03.630
That's why I want to meet him

17:03.630 --> 17:05.069
to explain it in person.

17:05.310 --> 17:05.910
I'm sorry.

17:06.000 --> 17:07.260
I really can't do that.

17:07.339 --> 17:09.859
You should probably
go back and wait for news.

17:08.400 --> 17:12.640
[Xingyao Smart Control]
[Yunzhi Pilot]

17:11.960 --> 17:15.000
Then please pass this on to him.

17:33.130 --> 17:33.990
Next one.

17:43.110 --> 17:45.240
I'm back, everyone.

17:45.240 --> 17:46.590
Zhenzhen!

17:46.590 --> 17:47.480
Here, for you.

17:47.880 --> 17:48.720
What is this?

17:48.720 --> 17:50.110
Zhenzhen, you're so generous.

17:50.110 --> 17:51.240
You shouldn't have.

17:51.350 --> 17:52.500
Congratulations, Zhenzhen.

17:52.500 --> 17:53.590
Thanks.

17:53.590 --> 17:54.200
Come on.

17:54.200 --> 17:54.880
Zhenzhen.

17:54.880 --> 17:55.750
Thanks.

17:55.750 --> 17:56.750
Help yourselves.

17:57.960 --> 17:58.830
Mr. Lin.

17:59.060 --> 18:00.060
Ms. Lu.

18:00.470 --> 18:01.790
You're back so soon.

18:02.070 --> 18:03.590
There are way too many eyes on me at home.

18:03.590 --> 18:05.320
It's way more relaxing at work.

18:07.480 --> 18:09.350
I heard Xu Miyu

18:09.350 --> 18:10.720
came to our department.

18:10.830 --> 18:11.590
Yep.

18:12.590 --> 18:14.350
She landed a small company deal

18:14.510 --> 18:17.200
and just got promoted to
the new business manager.

18:17.200 --> 18:18.800
She's in a meeting right now.

18:20.780 --> 18:22.040
What kind of business?

18:22.350 --> 18:23.830
Some AI

18:23.830 --> 18:24.830
company.

18:26.960 --> 18:27.850
This one.

18:30.860 --> 18:33.260
Sheng Yi Intelligent Technology Co., Ltd.

18:33.440 --> 18:34.700
100 room nights a year.

18:34.790 --> 18:35.790
Funny, right?

18:35.820 --> 18:37.590
I've never seen such a small order.

18:37.590 --> 18:39.350
The AI industry

18:39.350 --> 18:40.650
may be growing fast,

18:41.590 --> 18:42.880
and the market is big,

18:43.310 --> 18:44.440
but most of

18:44.440 --> 18:46.480
the companies are just getting started.

18:46.480 --> 18:48.580
They're extremely tight
on travel expenses,

18:48.580 --> 18:50.440
saving money to put back into R&D.

18:55.750 --> 18:57.070
Ms. Xu.

18:58.110 --> 18:59.270
Ms. Lu, you're back.

19:00.070 --> 19:03.120
I heard you took the high-tech track.

19:03.150 --> 19:03.930
Congratulations.

19:03.930 --> 19:04.820
Thank you.

19:05.350 --> 19:07.680
But the new business path
will be long and hard.

19:07.680 --> 19:08.750
Don't overwork yourself.

19:08.750 --> 19:10.730
I chose this path. It's not hard.

19:10.760 --> 19:12.670
You too. Take care.

19:22.560 --> 19:24.150
[Internal Affairs Office]

19:26.830 --> 19:28.750
Madam, I'd like to ask:

19:28.750 --> 19:31.600
why wasn't my application
for company anniversary gifts

19:31.600 --> 19:33.200
approved?

19:33.550 --> 19:34.510
Who are you?

19:35.000 --> 19:37.130
I am Xu Miyu, the new business manager.

19:49.590 --> 19:52.420
I have an appointment
with a client at 3:00 PM.

19:52.660 --> 19:54.040
I'm kind of in a hurry.

19:55.110 --> 19:57.920
Then what? Come back and ask another day?

19:58.920 --> 19:59.920
Take your time.

20:05.110 --> 20:06.310
This client of yours

20:06.310 --> 20:07.510
isn't qualified.

20:08.510 --> 20:09.750
Our department's

20:09.750 --> 20:11.750
gift management policy

20:11.880 --> 20:14.420
don't specify client qualifications.

20:14.450 --> 20:15.000
Besides,

20:15.000 --> 20:17.350
I only applied for
the most basic Class 3 gifts.

20:17.350 --> 20:19.070
Our department has never signed

20:19.070 --> 20:21.110
a deal for just 100 room nights a year.

20:21.110 --> 20:22.270
With such low profit

20:22.270 --> 20:23.550
spread over a year,

20:23.550 --> 20:25.510
it wouldn't even cover a Class 3 gift.

20:25.510 --> 20:27.510
But this client

20:27.510 --> 20:28.270
has introduced us

20:28.270 --> 20:30.880
to many potential clients
in the tech sector.

20:31.860 --> 20:33.740
They don't even deserve a Class 3 gift?

20:33.740 --> 20:34.930
If you think it's worth it,

20:34.930 --> 20:36.170
pay for it yourself.

20:36.200 --> 20:37.730
I'm just following policy.

20:41.790 --> 20:42.400
Thank you.

20:46.500 --> 20:47.630
You're here, right?

20:49.750 --> 20:51.270
I see you. I'm here.

20:53.880 --> 20:54.400
Over here.

20:54.400 --> 20:54.920
Your flowers.

20:54.920 --> 20:55.850
Okay, thank you.

20:56.890 --> 20:57.530
[Congratulations on Sheng Yi Intelligent
Technology's First Anniversary]

20:57.560 --> 20:58.150
[May Your Business Flourish
and Your Future]

20:58.180 --> 20:58.800
[Be Bright - Purong Hotel]

21:27.270 --> 21:28.000
Ms. Xu.

21:28.030 --> 21:28.830
Mr. Sheng.

21:28.870 --> 21:29.550
I'm sorry

21:29.550 --> 21:30.680
to keep you waiting.

21:30.920 --> 21:32.200
Long time no see, Mr. Sheng.

21:32.200 --> 21:33.110
I heard

21:33.160 --> 21:34.070
it's almost

21:34.070 --> 21:35.750
your company's first anniversary.

21:35.750 --> 21:38.590
I came specifically
to congratulate you. Here.

21:39.920 --> 21:41.240
Thank you.

21:41.350 --> 21:42.110
And most importantly,

21:42.110 --> 21:44.270
to thank you for giving Purong Hotel

21:44.310 --> 21:46.350
and me the opportunity to work with you.

21:46.350 --> 21:48.070
You're very thoughtful, Ms. Xu.

21:48.070 --> 21:49.990
You didn't mind our small order,

21:50.070 --> 21:51.680
and even brought a gift over.

21:51.920 --> 21:53.270
With that kind of sincerity,

21:53.270 --> 21:54.550
we have to work even harder.

21:54.550 --> 21:56.940
Let's aim for a big deal
in a couple of years.

21:56.940 --> 21:58.310
It's a deal then.

22:04.550 --> 22:05.350
Mr. Sheng,

22:05.890 --> 22:07.410
is that

22:06.900 --> 22:07.360
[VIP Room]

22:07.440 --> 22:09.370
Mr. Lu from Lubot Company in there?

22:09.720 --> 22:11.280
[VIP Room]

22:09.920 --> 22:11.510
Yes. Do you know each other?

22:11.750 --> 22:12.790
To be honest,

22:12.930 --> 22:14.310
I'm now working on

22:14.310 --> 22:16.350
a cooperation project with Lubot Company.

22:16.350 --> 22:17.520
What a coincidence.

22:17.640 --> 22:19.640
We've been close friends for years.

22:20.390 --> 22:21.590
Let me introduce you.

22:21.590 --> 22:22.640
Okay. Thank you.

22:25.510 --> 22:26.310
Mr. Lu.

22:37.810 --> 22:39.920
[Report]

22:39.940 --> 22:42.440
[Xu Miyu
Daily Work Summary: Work Overview]

22:44.860 --> 22:45.950
[Xu Miyu
Daily Work Summary]

22:45.970 --> 22:47.250
[Work Overview: Over the past two weeks,]

22:47.270 --> 22:48.920
[I've actively expanded my business
and achieved significant results.]

22:50.970 --> 22:52.470
[II. Business development:]

22:52.490 --> 22:53.330
[1. Cooperation with
Sheng Yi Intelligent Technology Co., Ltd]

22:54.490 --> 22:55.660
[2. Contact with
Lubot Intelligent Storm Technology]

22:55.680 --> 22:56.690
[Co., Ltd.]

23:00.790 --> 23:03.830
What? Lubot is contacting Purong?

23:04.640 --> 23:05.550
When did this happen?

23:05.550 --> 23:08.510
It's Xu Miyu
from the sales department leading it.

23:12.700 --> 23:14.430
How dare she steal my business?

23:15.550 --> 23:16.550
Redo the quotation.

23:16.550 --> 23:17.030
Okay.

23:17.030 --> 23:18.290
Lower it by another 5%.

23:18.590 --> 23:19.590
By today.

23:19.750 --> 23:20.310
Okay.

23:21.070 --> 23:22.470
What are you waiting for?

23:26.820 --> 23:28.070
Xu Miyu.

23:29.120 --> 23:30.380
I underestimated you.

23:30.920 --> 23:32.000
[Part 1: Overall Venue Layout]

23:32.240 --> 23:37.850
[Overall Venue Layout]

23:33.590 --> 23:35.110
Based on your company's

23:35.130 --> 23:37.130
third-generation Smart Agibot,

23:37.160 --> 23:38.830
we've also made some

23:38.830 --> 23:40.510
groundbreaking designs

23:40.510 --> 23:42.600
for the launch event.

23:42.830 --> 23:43.790
For example,

23:43.370 --> 23:52.280
[Product Display Area]

23:46.000 --> 23:48.400
we'll expand the display area,

23:48.400 --> 23:50.350
allowing customers to experience

23:50.350 --> 23:52.590
the Agibot's unique features up close.

23:53.200 --> 23:53.830
Also,

23:53.730 --> 23:55.070
[Product Display Area]

23:53.830 --> 23:57.070
we'll have a lounge and meeting area.

23:55.780 --> 23:56.960
[Lounge & Meeting Area]

23:57.080 --> 24:00.080
Any customer who's interested

24:00.110 --> 24:02.200
in the product after seeing it

24:00.200 --> 24:05.710
[Entrance Reception Area]
[Lounge & Meeting Area]

24:02.200 --> 24:03.400
can have

24:03.400 --> 24:04.350
in-depth discussions

24:04.350 --> 24:05.830
with our staff on the spot.

24:05.830 --> 24:06.680
In this area,

24:06.680 --> 24:08.110
we'll create a more

24:08.110 --> 24:10.370
comfortable and relaxing environment.

24:16.630 --> 24:18.710
[Report]

24:21.190 --> 24:22.470
[Notify] [Wan Shunzhi] [Xu Miyu]

24:23.730 --> 24:24.330
[Xu Miyu
Daily Work Summary]

24:24.370 --> 24:25.710
[Work Item:
Lubot Intelligent Storm Technology's]

24:25.740 --> 24:27.370
[New Generation Smart Agibot]

24:27.400 --> 24:29.580
[Presale Event Proposal
Consultation Meeting]

24:37.000 --> 24:37.750
Come in.

24:38.880 --> 24:39.840
Hello, Mr. Ji.

24:39.670 --> 24:42.270
[Purong Hotel]

24:41.770 --> 24:42.640
Ms. Lu.

24:46.160 --> 24:46.680
Mr. Ji,

24:46.920 --> 24:48.030
I want to talk to you

24:48.030 --> 24:50.160
about the Lubot project. Is that okay?

24:50.920 --> 24:52.670
What's your take?

24:52.880 --> 24:54.160
I know this product launch

24:54.160 --> 24:55.830
has a huge impact on this industry.

24:55.830 --> 24:57.590
It's a big event—hundreds of people,

24:57.590 --> 24:59.830
including audience
members, media, clients,

24:59.830 --> 25:01.180
and the company's own staff.

25:01.180 --> 25:02.270
It's a massive deal.

25:02.270 --> 25:03.350
A single mistake

25:03.350 --> 25:04.640
would be a huge loss

25:04.640 --> 25:06.170
for both Lubot

25:06.350 --> 25:07.830
and Purong Hotel.

25:08.000 --> 25:09.920
I've also worked with a

25:09.950 --> 25:11.350
smart healthcare company before,

25:11.350 --> 25:12.680
so I have some understanding

25:12.680 --> 25:14.070
of the AI industry.

25:14.070 --> 25:16.000
That's why I'd like to request

25:16.000 --> 25:17.880
to join this project team

25:17.880 --> 25:20.310
and assist Ms. Xu with this case.

25:20.870 --> 25:22.620
How do you plan to assist?

25:22.640 --> 25:23.640
I'm confident

25:23.640 --> 25:24.840
in client relations.

25:25.000 --> 25:26.440
Mr. Ji, if you can

25:26.460 --> 25:28.700
introduce me to Mr. Lu from Lubot,

25:28.750 --> 25:29.440
I guarantee

25:29.440 --> 25:30.920
I'll make him have a better impression

25:30.920 --> 25:32.000
of Purong Hotel.

25:32.150 --> 25:35.300
And I'll strive to secure
a long-term agreement with Lubot.

25:35.300 --> 25:36.880
As for Ms. Xu,

25:36.880 --> 25:38.160
please rest assured.

25:38.160 --> 25:39.680
I definitely won't steal her credit.

25:39.680 --> 25:40.440
She'll still

25:40.440 --> 25:42.510
be leading our project team.

25:42.640 --> 25:44.910
She just won't
have to go it alone anymore.

25:44.910 --> 25:46.690
If anything unexpected comes up,

25:46.690 --> 25:48.970
I'll be there to help her

25:48.990 --> 25:49.990
manage the risks.

25:51.270 --> 25:52.030
Is that so?

25:53.000 --> 25:54.030
I see you still have

25:54.030 --> 25:56.230
quite a few client complaints piled up.

25:57.470 --> 25:58.670
Well,

25:59.270 --> 26:01.510
those clients

26:01.530 --> 26:02.640
have been pretty difficult lately.

26:02.640 --> 26:03.480
So I figured,

26:03.500 --> 26:06.350
if I want to create
the most value for the hotel,

26:06.350 --> 26:09.110
I should be ready
to switch tracks at any time.

26:09.160 --> 26:10.510
Please don't worry, Mr. Ji.

26:10.510 --> 26:12.510
I'll smooth things over
with my existing clients.

26:12.510 --> 26:14.350
It won't affect
the new project's operation.

26:14.350 --> 26:16.350
I'd rather you not move so fast.

26:16.750 --> 26:18.640
Pick a lane and go deep.

26:18.640 --> 26:20.040
Show some results first.

26:24.160 --> 26:25.110
You're right, Mr. Ji.

26:25.110 --> 26:27.240
I'll deal with my client issues first.

26:27.440 --> 26:28.270
Organize and wrap up

26:28.270 --> 26:30.150
the projects you're currently

26:30.350 --> 26:31.310
handling.

26:32.350 --> 26:33.750
As for the Lubot project,

26:33.750 --> 26:36.510
let Ms. Xu get some practice on it.

26:38.110 --> 26:38.640
Okay.

26:39.250 --> 26:41.210
If you need me for the new project,

26:41.240 --> 26:42.640
just let me know anytime.

26:42.660 --> 26:43.100
Okay.

26:54.490 --> 26:55.110
Mr. Lu,

26:55.110 --> 26:56.110
rest assured.

26:56.590 --> 26:58.520
I will double-check the contract.

27:03.030 --> 27:04.310
No trouble at all.

27:04.310 --> 27:06.070
It's our job to verify the details.

27:06.070 --> 27:07.830
I'll go over the contract again tonight,

27:07.830 --> 27:09.350
and send the final version to Manager Wu

27:09.350 --> 27:10.840
for confirmation, okay?

27:10.860 --> 27:12.550
Alright. See you tomorrow at 9 AM.

27:12.550 --> 27:14.030
Please give me a few more clues.

27:14.030 --> 27:17.030
I've been waiting for
Mr. Zhang for almost a month now.

27:47.110 --> 27:48.160
Ms. Lu?

27:50.680 --> 27:52.130
Mr. Duan.

27:52.830 --> 27:53.750
Hello.

27:53.750 --> 27:54.740
What's wrong?

27:55.510 --> 27:56.270
My car's

27:56.590 --> 27:58.170
tire is a bit flat,

27:58.510 --> 28:00.590
but I have to meet a client right now.

28:00.640 --> 28:01.510
Where to?

28:01.640 --> 28:02.590
Pudong.

28:02.670 --> 28:04.350
Let's go. I'll give you a ride.

28:04.350 --> 28:05.330
Thank you.

28:54.180 --> 28:56.330
[Lu Zhenzhen]

29:01.590 --> 29:02.680
Hello, Ms. Lu?

29:02.680 --> 29:05.240
Ms. Xu, did you check the group chat?

29:08.830 --> 29:09.830
Here's the thing.

29:10.350 --> 29:11.590
Could you please

29:11.590 --> 29:13.390
go to Jiqing Chemical tomorrow?

29:22.160 --> 29:24.960
Their boss is coming back tonight

29:25.590 --> 29:27.880
and will leave for a business trip
early tomorrow morning.

29:27.880 --> 29:29.030
Our department has some documents

29:29.030 --> 29:31.160
that must be handed to him personally.

29:32.640 --> 29:34.160
No one else is available.

29:34.590 --> 29:36.920
I have to accompany a client
to the development zone early tomorrow.

29:36.920 --> 29:38.780
I can only ask you to make the trip.

29:44.590 --> 29:47.120
You have another
contract signing tomorrow?

29:47.790 --> 29:49.990
Can you reschedule it to the afternoon?

29:51.350 --> 29:52.510
I'm sorry.

29:53.830 --> 29:54.590
Alright.

29:54.830 --> 29:55.590
Great.

29:56.160 --> 29:57.920
I'll send you the materials later.

29:57.920 --> 29:59.380
Please review them for me.

30:00.410 --> 30:01.920
Thanks. Appreciate it.

30:17.900 --> 30:19.220
[Lu Zhenzhen]
[Jiqing Chemical Conference Layout Draft]

30:50.910 --> 30:52.440
[Sales Office]

30:52.810 --> 30:55.060
[Jiqing Chemical
Conference Activity Process]

31:48.920 --> 31:50.440
It really is Mr. Lu's car.

31:50.480 --> 31:51.330
Mr. Duan,

31:51.440 --> 31:52.680
Ms. Lu said

31:52.700 --> 31:54.880
that Xu Miyu's already
arrived at Jiqing Chemical.

31:54.880 --> 31:57.150
The signing will probably
be this afternoon.

31:57.150 --> 31:58.920
Please make good use of these three hours.

31:58.920 --> 32:00.000
I wish you success.

32:00.280 --> 32:01.990
Three hours is way too long.

32:02.090 --> 32:02.850
Let's go.

32:04.080 --> 32:04.900
[Purong Hotel
Accommodation & Event Service Contract]

32:07.520 --> 32:08.560
[Party A: Lubot
Intelligent Storm Technology Co., Ltd.]

32:08.590 --> 32:09.190
[Party B: Purong Hotel Co., Ltd.]

32:09.210 --> 32:09.940
[Authorized Representative : Xu Miyu]

32:10.130 --> 32:11.270
What's going on here?

32:11.270 --> 32:12.510
You didn't go to Jiqing Chemical?

32:12.510 --> 32:13.290
I did.

32:13.590 --> 32:14.640
I delivered the documents.

32:14.640 --> 32:16.210
Then when did you sign with Lubot?

32:16.210 --> 32:17.690
Isn't there a date on it?

32:24.160 --> 32:24.680
Mr. Duan.

32:24.680 --> 32:26.520
Lu Zhenzhen, get over here!

32:28.920 --> 32:30.540
Let me explain, Mr. Duan.

32:45.830 --> 32:48.440
Xu Miyu, just you wait.

32:59.260 --> 33:01.880
[Mr. Lu]

33:04.950 --> 33:10.490
[Mr. Lu]

33:10.830 --> 33:11.340
[Mr. Sheng]

33:16.400 --> 33:17.830
Hello, Ms. Xu?

33:17.880 --> 33:18.680
Hello?

33:19.110 --> 33:21.070
Mr. Sheng, I'm sorry.

33:21.070 --> 33:22.550
I didn't mean to disturb you so late.

33:22.550 --> 33:23.350
Disturb?

33:23.790 --> 33:24.390
Not at all.

33:24.790 --> 33:26.160
We're having a dinner party.

33:26.160 --> 33:27.840
Come and join us.

33:28.310 --> 33:29.640
No, thank you.

33:29.830 --> 33:31.310
I was just wondering

33:31.310 --> 33:33.270
if you know where Mr. Lu is.

33:34.030 --> 33:34.830
Wait a moment.

33:36.270 --> 33:36.990
Hello?

33:37.490 --> 33:38.650
H-Hello?

33:39.310 --> 33:39.920
Hello?

33:39.920 --> 33:41.140
Is this Ms. Xu?

33:41.170 --> 33:42.350
Mr. Lu?

33:42.370 --> 33:43.110
Sorry,

33:43.110 --> 33:44.550
I didn't have my phone on me.

33:44.550 --> 33:45.830
What's up?

33:45.830 --> 33:46.550
It's fine.

33:46.550 --> 33:47.830
I just wanted to tell you

33:47.830 --> 33:51.350
-about tomorrow's signing. I...
-Come and tell me in person.

33:51.350 --> 33:52.920
We're all good friends here.

33:52.920 --> 33:54.110
You must come.

33:54.130 --> 33:55.530
We'll be waiting for you.

34:00.030 --> 34:00.960
Top sales rep,

34:00.960 --> 34:02.820
why are you working so late again?

34:02.830 --> 34:04.630
You must not have had dinner yet.

34:05.160 --> 34:07.110
I-I'm in a hurry to meet a client.

34:07.830 --> 34:09.510
What client? Where?

34:09.550 --> 34:10.440
I can't talk right now.

34:10.440 --> 34:11.590
I really have to go.

34:11.590 --> 34:12.760
I'll report to you tomorrow, okay?

34:12.760 --> 34:13.510
Bye.

34:15.400 --> 34:16.600
Tell me before you go.

34:17.590 --> 34:19.360
It's Mr. Lu from Lubot.

34:19.360 --> 34:21.300
We were supposed
to sign tomorrow morning,

34:21.300 --> 34:23.400
but something urgent came up for me.

34:23.400 --> 34:25.360
And it turns out Mr. Lu's free tonight.

34:25.360 --> 34:26.590
So you're in a hurry to sign?

34:26.590 --> 34:27.320
They're having dinner.

34:27.320 --> 34:28.840
I'll see if I have a chance
to get it signed.

34:28.840 --> 34:30.000
So you're going

34:30.000 --> 34:31.460
to their dinner right now?

34:32.670 --> 34:34.070
Do you know
how many people will be there?

34:34.070 --> 34:34.840
No.

34:34.860 --> 34:35.670
Does anyone else

34:35.670 --> 34:37.070
know about this besides me?

34:37.070 --> 34:38.000
No.

34:38.000 --> 34:39.730
Do you think you can pull it off?

34:40.590 --> 34:41.190
I...

34:41.510 --> 34:42.420
I didn't think that much.

34:42.420 --> 34:44.880
A top sales rep
hits the target with one shot.

34:47.590 --> 34:48.320
Let's go.

34:48.320 --> 34:49.110
Where to?

34:49.510 --> 34:51.000
I'll go with you.

34:56.670 --> 34:57.590
Impressive.

34:58.400 --> 35:00.250
Truly impressive.

35:00.510 --> 35:03.240
So you came up with this scheme
to turn the tables.

35:03.360 --> 35:04.190
Tell me the truth.

35:04.190 --> 35:05.280
That night,

35:05.280 --> 35:07.070
did you deliberately
hide at the hotel's back door

35:07.070 --> 35:08.150
to be her knight in shining armor?

35:08.150 --> 35:09.360
I went with her

35:09.360 --> 35:11.150
to get the deal signed.

35:11.150 --> 35:12.190
Got a problem with that?

35:12.190 --> 35:13.190
Not at all.

35:13.280 --> 35:15.360
It's brilliant. And handsome too.

35:18.280 --> 35:18.840
Come in.

35:18.840 --> 35:19.590
Mr. Ji,

35:19.590 --> 35:21.110
the banquet hall is ready.

35:21.110 --> 35:22.670
Ms. Xu is already there.

35:23.030 --> 35:24.630
Okay, we'll be right there.

35:24.800 --> 35:25.510
Thanks for your hard work.

35:25.510 --> 35:26.240
It's my duty.

35:33.670 --> 35:36.320
Dating really changes a person.

35:46.840 --> 35:47.760
Agibot,

35:47.780 --> 35:50.580
are you satisfied with
today's pre-launch event?

35:50.580 --> 35:52.670
This event is truly a great success.

35:52.670 --> 35:53.590
I love it.

35:54.100 --> 35:56.210
It's so smart.

35:56.440 --> 36:00.100
But just like good flavor requires
more than just good technique—

36:00.230 --> 36:01.590
it needs personality,

36:01.670 --> 36:02.590
awareness,

36:02.590 --> 36:03.510
and aesthetics.

36:03.510 --> 36:05.100
AI still has a long way to go

36:05.100 --> 36:07.060
when it comes to creativity.

36:07.230 --> 36:08.800
Take this little pastry, for example.

36:08.800 --> 36:10.440
To truly win over diners,

36:10.630 --> 36:12.320
AI would have to study it for a long time.

36:12.320 --> 36:13.230
Indeed.

36:13.320 --> 36:14.510
The warmth of craftsmanship

36:14.510 --> 36:16.320
often requires years of refinement.

36:16.320 --> 36:18.670
But AI works nonstop.

36:18.760 --> 36:22.410
It can be more efficient and more
precise in improving productivity.

36:22.410 --> 36:24.110
Coming to this launch event today,

36:24.110 --> 36:25.320
I'm even more convinced

36:25.320 --> 36:26.070
that nothing

36:26.070 --> 36:28.070
can stop this era from arriving.

36:31.320 --> 36:32.510
A superior and subordinate

36:32.510 --> 36:34.840
who work together so seamlessly like you.

36:35.630 --> 36:36.690
I really envy that.

36:38.320 --> 36:39.320
I mean,

36:39.440 --> 36:42.070
that kind of work environment
is the best for cultivating talent.

36:42.070 --> 36:43.070
Ms. Xu is

36:43.070 --> 36:44.030
nothing like any other

36:44.030 --> 36:45.330
salesperson I've met.

36:45.580 --> 36:48.190
I often find myself
guessing what she'll do next.

36:48.190 --> 36:49.670
I've been trying to figure her out,

36:49.670 --> 36:51.320
only to realize
she has no ulterior motive at all.

36:51.320 --> 36:52.580
Did you teach her that?

36:54.670 --> 36:55.880
I get it.

36:55.880 --> 36:58.680
Mr. Lu saying is that
I'm not professional enough.

36:59.590 --> 37:01.120
It's called being relaxed.

37:01.320 --> 37:03.920
Mr. Ji, you should know
what I'm talking about.

37:05.150 --> 37:06.440
Our Ms. Xu is indeed

37:06.440 --> 37:08.440
different from other salespeople.

37:08.670 --> 37:10.790
She is not the aggressive type.

37:11.110 --> 37:12.710
Kind of like how I feel about Kuanli—

37:12.710 --> 37:14.380
solid but rigid.

37:14.510 --> 37:17.080
There's a strange arrogance to it.

37:17.320 --> 37:20.230
Large groups have a habit
of choosing the people,

37:20.230 --> 37:21.630
not the other way around.

37:22.190 --> 37:23.190
At Purong Hotel,

37:23.190 --> 37:25.400
we also strive for high

37:25.400 --> 37:26.530
and high standards.

37:26.590 --> 37:28.030
But by "high," we don't mean

37:28.030 --> 37:30.070
being harsh to our employees

37:30.070 --> 37:32.030
or filtering our clients.

37:32.630 --> 37:34.630
Then what kind of "high" do you mean?

37:35.590 --> 37:38.990
It's the kind where your feet lift
half an inch off the ground.

37:42.880 --> 37:44.030
W-What do you mean?

37:44.200 --> 37:45.600
What I mean is,

37:45.630 --> 37:48.150
we want every guest
who walks into Purong Hotel

37:48.150 --> 37:49.320
to feel that little lift—

37:49.320 --> 37:51.980
the joy of being
half an inch off the ground.

37:52.070 --> 37:55.070
It's not a life-changing feeling,

37:55.070 --> 37:55.710
but rather a way

37:55.710 --> 37:58.280
for people to temporarily detach

37:58.280 --> 37:59.630
from real life,

37:59.630 --> 38:00.960
and then discover that

38:00.960 --> 38:03.090
there is a life worth longing for here.

38:03.190 --> 38:04.840
A like worth longing for.

38:04.960 --> 38:06.160
That's my slogan too.

38:06.440 --> 38:08.120
It knows again.

38:08.230 --> 38:09.880
After going around in circles,

38:09.880 --> 38:12.540
it turns out we want the same thing.

38:13.590 --> 38:15.030
Even though

38:15.030 --> 38:16.710
tech research and service seem to be

38:16.710 --> 38:18.150
two unrelated industries,

38:18.150 --> 38:21.030
what we do is actually similar.

38:21.190 --> 38:22.880
We're both dedicated to

38:22.880 --> 38:25.480
making small improvements
in people's lives.

38:25.710 --> 38:26.670
Well said.

38:26.800 --> 38:27.510
Our Lubot

38:27.510 --> 38:29.960
is fairly successful

38:29.960 --> 38:31.590
in China's AI industry,

38:31.590 --> 38:32.110
but

38:32.110 --> 38:35.030
compared to tycoons in other industries,

38:35.030 --> 38:36.600
we're still small in scale

38:37.030 --> 38:38.290
and limited in budget.

38:39.230 --> 38:40.880
I understand that different industries

38:40.880 --> 38:43.030
have vastly different business models

38:43.030 --> 38:44.510
and consumer habits.

38:44.590 --> 38:45.230
We will absolutely not use

38:45.230 --> 38:46.510
service standards from other industries

38:46.510 --> 38:49.310
to presume your company's
concerns and troubles.

38:49.400 --> 38:51.200
You can rest assured about that.

38:51.880 --> 38:52.710
Good.

38:52.710 --> 38:54.230
I'll have my assistant

38:54.230 --> 38:56.110
send over our company's
specific requirements later.

38:56.110 --> 38:57.670
Then we'll schedule

38:57.670 --> 39:00.230
a meeting with representatives
from the other departments.

39:00.230 --> 39:02.400
Okay. Thank you for your trust, Mr. Lu.

39:02.400 --> 39:05.110
I won't let you down.

39:05.760 --> 39:06.590
Glad to work with you.

39:06.590 --> 39:07.190
Thank you.

39:08.320 --> 39:09.310
You have to take

39:09.800 --> 39:11.530
personal charge of my company.

39:12.070 --> 39:12.960
It's my honor.

39:15.510 --> 39:15.960
Come on.

39:15.960 --> 39:18.590
Let's take a photo with Agibot together.

39:18.590 --> 39:19.880
-The four of us.
-Okay.

39:20.110 --> 39:21.220
Here, use my phone.

39:23.550 --> 39:24.280
Come on.

39:25.110 --> 39:26.760
Three, two, one.
